OL,3,CCharles and Camilla thought White
OL,4,CHouse was 'amazing', says US president
OL,6,FThe King and Queen thought the White
OL,7,FHouse was "amazing", Donald Trump has
OL,8,Fsaid while noting they have "seen some
OL,9,Fvery nice places".
OL,11,FThe US president also said Charles and
OL,12,FCamilla had been very impressed with
OL,13,Fthe Oval Office, during their recent
OL,14,Fstate visit.
OL,16,FMr Trump revealed the royal couple's
OL,17,Fviews as he welcomed small business
OL,18,Fowners to the official residence in
OL,19,FWashington DC.
