OL,3,CCharles and Camilla thought White
OL,4,CHouse was 'amazing', says US president
OL,6,FThe King and Queen concluded their
OL,7,Fwhistlestop four-day trip to the US to
OL,8,Fmark the 250th anniversary of American
OL,9,Findependence last Thursday.
OL,11,FTheir frenetic schedule ranged from
OL,12,Ftaking tea at the White House with Mr
OL,13,FTrump and his wife Melania, a white-
OL,14,Ftie banquet in their honour, a
OL,15,Fhistoric address to Congress and a
OL,16,Fbunting-decked street party in rural
OL,17,FVirginia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
