OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777943047
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla thought White
OL,4,CHouse was 'amazing', says US president
OL,6,FThe soft power charm offensive, coming
OL,7,Famid fractious transatlantic relations
OL,8,Fover the Iran war, paid off with the
OL,9,Fpresident announcing the removal of
OL,10,Ftariffs on Scotch whisky, in a major
OL,11,Fboost for the industry.
OL,13,FHosting a small business summit on
OL,14,FMonday, Mr Trump said: "I'm thrilled
OL,15,Fto be with you and welcome you to the
OL,16,Fmost fabulous place, the White House.
OL,18,F"There is nothing quite like it.
OL,19,FPeople come from all over the world.
OL,26,@vD@XOUzD@AOU
