OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777943047
OL,3,CCharles and Camilla thought White
OL,4,CHouse was 'amazing', says US president
OL,6,F"The King and Queen were just here,
OL,7,Fand they looked and they said, 'This
OL,8,Fplace is just amazing'.
OL,10,F"When they came into the Oval Office,
OL,11,Fthey said, 'This is something'. And
OL,12,Fthey've seen some very nice places.
OL,13,FThey've seen some great rooms, but it
OL,14,Fis a very special place."
